{ Modules

 `‚Üí Linux/fhs/proc/asound/modules` shows the loaded sound ‚Üí Linux/kernel/module[module] (along with their order).

  Alternatively, `‚Üí Linux/shell/commands/lsmod | grep snd` gets a devices and modules list (snd = for sound cards?)

  Apparently, the standard module for *on-board cards* is `snd_hda_intel`.

}
